  "text": "The conceptual framework for the current analysis was modified from the ecological model of childhood obesity of Davison and Birch [CITATION_1] to include not only the available variables in the IFLS data set, but also stunting as a form of malnutrition. The potential risk factors were divided into three categories: child-, parental-and household-, and community-level factors.",
